title: Olympic National Park: Scout Groups
body: Explore This Park    Get Involved     Volunteer     Scout Groups              Scout Opportunities          Be a Scout Ranger! Girl Scouts and Boy Scouts can participate in this special youth program. Olympic National Park is a great place to complete your service project. Please contact Heather Stephens, Volunteer and Youth Coordinator to schedule your project. Heather can be reached at: (360) 565-3141 or at Heather_Stephens@nps.gov. Please allow a minimum of four weeks to schedule a group specific event.
